20.	Count how many total combinations of employees and departments exist.
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_combinations
    -> FROM Employees e
    -> CROSS JOIN Departments d;
+--------------------+
| total_combinations |
+--------------------+
|                 48 |
+--------------------+
